—
</emphasis>
Atlantic and Pacific slopes of 
<collectingCountry id="2ADBCCDA5251FFEEB3B9CB1DFCDFE090" box="[722,845,618,642]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
and 
